    <scopecontent id="aspace_4ae75694fb828f53fe3ed7cc0053ac38">
      <head>Scope and Contents</head>
      <p>The four scrapbooks that make up this collection contain clippings, programs, and photographs documenting the successes and failures of the Metropolitan Police Department. Also included in these scrapbooks are clippings related to the King and Queen of England.</p>
    </scopecontent>
    <userestrict id="aspace_034f34a2a410e89ca4a294848685cdaa">
